show.description: Beneath the flawless makeup of Rose Beauty lies a sinister secret. The Rosy Psycho peels back the glossy façade to reveal obsession, betrayal, and a haunting past that refuses to stay buried. It's beauty versus madness only one will survive. Watch Now.
